T02TD3367E:42a-1: ku ru kulle s'a dha nam /
T02TD3367E:42a-3: lha mo rigs byed ma'i sgrub pa'i thabs /
T02TD3367E:42a-4: lha mo rigs byed ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3367E:42a-5: dang por bde ba'i gdan la 'dug ste /
T02TD3367E:42a-6: rigs byed ma'i gzugs su byas nas sems can ma lus pa dbang du bya ba brtsam par bya'o //
T02TD3367E:42a-7: rang gi snying gar nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor ro //
T02TD3367E:42a-8: de'i steng du tr'am dmar po'o //
T02TD3367E:42a-9: de nas 'od zer rnam pa lnga byung ste /
T02TD3367E:42a-10: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams yang dag par mchod pa /
T02TD3367E:42b-0: dkon @42b mchog gsum la skyabs su mchi //
T02TD3367E:42b-1: zhes bya ba la sogs pas sdig pa bshags pa la sogs pa byas la /
T02TD3367E:42b-2: stong pa nyid kyi rnam pa bsgoms la /
T02TD3367E:42b-3: phyis ni autpa la dmar po /
T02TD3367E:42b-4: de'i steng du nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor de'i steng du aam dmar po /
T02TD3367E:42b-5: 'di thams cad yongs su gyur pa las rigs byed ma rje btsun mdog dkar zhing dmar ba phyag bzhi pa /
T02TD3367E:42b-6: g-yas pa'i phyag na mda' dang mi 'jigs pa sbyin pa'i phyag go //
T02TD3367E:42b-7: g-yon pa na gzhu dang autpa la bsnams pa'o //
T02TD3367E:42b-8: rdo rje skyil mo krung gis gnas shing sha 'gag dmar po dang /
T02TD3367E:42b-9: stod g-yogs dmar po can gyi rnam par bsgom par bya'o //
T02TD3367E:42b-10: 'og tu 'dod pa'i lha chung ma dang bcas pa bsams te /
T02TD3367E:42b-11: phyi nas bsgom pa dang ldan pas sngags kyi bzlas pa bya'o //
T02TD3367E:42b-12: aom ku ru kulle sv'a h'a /
T02TD3367E:42b-13: rigs byed ma'i sgrub thabs rdzogs so //
T02TD3367E:42b-14: pandi ta don yod rdo rje dang /
T02TD3367E:42b-15: khams pa lo ts'a ba dge slong ba ris bsgyur ba'o//
